      "content": "thanks. the heating pad sounds okay but the pain is actually getting kinda intense now, like it's making it hard to even stand up straight. i really don't want to go to the hospital or anything because it's so expensive and i just want to sleep. if i take a double dose of the ibuprofen it would probably handle it better, right? and is it safe to eat something light like toast before i take them just so my stomach isn't empty?",
